ji\" /> 安全D好"},{"pid":"ea14565e810434d5493427af59e52b22902884f9","tid":311565,"uid":60967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"好多人唔識較鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊鏡係用黎睇出面情況，你睇自己車做乜柒"},{"pid":"f96de4325f3c60ddd5c9e04b97f78ae52e8d8418","tid":311565,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多人唔識較鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊鏡係用黎睇出面情況，你睇自己車做乜柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家D鏡好似有兩截, 近車果截可以較到望到車身, 出面果截睇正常後方<br />\n<br />\n塊鏡較得啱睇鏡就得, 咁如果你話你揸泥頭車冇野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e9ff560fa7d6a016bfb99384f0042e1a0eec26","tid":311565,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n試過差啲收26皮"},{"pid":"1b7313996237b96e43c09a7d893ec72f52e974a9","tid":311565,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"同開門一樣 點都要望左先 又唔係辛苦野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8decd14868699747123c77107285e76d14b02a22","tid":311565,"uid":24870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T00:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多人唔識較鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊鏡係用黎睇出面情況，你睇自己車做乜柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家D鏡好似有兩截, 近車果截可以較到望到車身, 出面果截睇正常後方<br />\n<br />\n塊鏡較得啱睇鏡就得, 咁如果你話你揸泥頭車冇野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢種係咪私家車短車較法？ 我見一般中型或者客貨車都應該要睇到自己個尾"},{"pid":"eef111d8217104fec4397d6996f5100f7a3c0c2e","tid":311565,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T00:39:35.000Z","msg":"琴日揸26，明明記得右邊鏡好似有架van,跟住再望望鏡就唔見左，擰一擰先見到。如果要轉線唔望盲點就會撞。<br />\n唔望除非你係咁望鏡，記得晒d車咩位置"},{"pid":"f75094699802ad23a93d5eb6a754a243bc91a973","tid":311565,"uid":54617,"